Class JsonIntRealBoolRunnable

  • java.lang.Object
    • haskellapi.jsonrunnables.JsonPrimitiveArrayRunnable
      • haskellapi.jsonrunnables.JsonPrimitiveRunnable
        • haskellapi.jsonrunnables.JsonIntRealBoolRunnable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JsonRunnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    JsonAccumulatorRunnable, JsonLoggerRunnable

    public abstract class JsonIntRealBoolRunnable
extends JsonPrimitiveRunnable
    A JsonRunnable which only runs through integers, real numbers and booleans. It also runs through such primitives inside arrays.
